name: Ciao Mamma#2  (2008)
description:
Screenprinting with acrylics on three colours. (Somerset paper)

Limited edition of 50 artworks. A previous edition (all sold out) featured in many exhibition promoted by the East London Printmakers studio.

Size: 17x17cm. All works are with mountboard, backboard and transparent envelope.

Works can be purchased framed or unframed.

name: China 1939  -  (2007)
description:
Limited edition of 30 artprints. (First edition). 

Screenprinting, oil pastels, pens on paper.
Size: 20x25cm (aperture image 12.5 x17.5 cm). 

Available in bigger size (on request)

Available on giclee' print, signed and numbered in a limited edition (first edition) of 20. Price for giclee' print is £8 only. 

All Prints (any kind) comes with mount-board, back-board and transparent envelope.
